<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4532589>
    dc:description "Figure 1-4. Tibial types. 1) Rhyparus-type mesotibia, male Rhyparus mexicanus Cartwright and Woodruff. 2) Termitodiellus-type mesotibia, male Termitodiellus luzonensis (Howden). 3) Termitodius-type mesotibia, male Aschnarhyparus peregrinus (Hinton). 4) Termitodius-type mesotibia, male Termitodius araujoi Reyes-Castillo and Martinez. Line = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4532589/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

